bio: I have been a hairdresser for over 12 years and love creating new pieces of art on people's heads!
If you need a haircut, I am your girl! :-) I love cutting hair!
Have you ever wondered what a good haircut really is? Well stop asking yourself that ridiculous question and see for yourself by booking an appointment with me!
I have many years experience and cut hair good. I am from Russia originally and try make good business here in America.
